item.title: CVE-2021-20026|2024-08-03T17:30:07.526Z -- sonicwall -- sonicwall%20nsm%20on-prem
item.description: A vulnerability in the SonicWall NSM On-Prem product allows an authenticated attacker to perform OS command injection using a crafted HTTP request. This vulnerability affects NSM On-Prem 2.2.0-R10 and earlier versions.
